Stage 1
Collect weight from user 
Collect height 
Convert them to kilo and meters
Calculate BMI 
Display the result

Stage2 
Ask user to enter weight 
Collect weight of user 
Store the weight in weigthInput
Ask user to enter height 
Collect height of user 
Store the height in heigthInput
Convert weight to kilogram using  weigthInput * 0.45359237
Store in weight
Convert height tp meters using  heigthInput * 0.0254
Store in height calculate BMI using weight / (height * height)
Store in BMI 
Print the result 